OL,3,CMan who pioneered space communications
OL,4,Cin Cornwall awarded OBE
OL,6,FThe founder of Goonhilly Earth Station
OL,7,FLtd, based in Cornwall, has been
OL,8,Fawarded an OBE for his services to
OL,9,Fspace communications.
OL,11,FIan Jones said it was a "surprise" to
OL,12,Freceive the award and be recognised
OL,13,Ffor his contribution to the industry.
OL,15,FHe told ITV West Country: "We were
OL,16,Fexpecting to receive a contract from
OL,17,Fthe government for some services that
OL,18,FGoonhilly were providing.
