OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1718567067
OL,3,CMan who pioneered space communications
OL,4,Cin Cornwall awarded OBE
OL,6,F"My wife called me and said there's a
OL,7,Fvery official looking letter at home,
OL,8,Fyou better come and take a look.
OL,10,F"What a surprise to have received an
OL,11,FOBE. Absolutely fantastic.
OL,13,F"To be recognised by my country, and
OL,14,Fby my peers in the industry, it is
OL,15,Fvery special."
OL,17,FGoonhilly Earth Station might be close
OL,18,Fto home, on the Lizard, but it's
OL,19,Fpresence is now recognised across the
OL,20,Fglobe.
