OL,3,CMan who pioneered space communications
OL,4,Cin Cornwall awarded OBE
OL,6,FIt provides the means of communication
OL,7,Fbetween spacecraft and the ground -
OL,8,Fand as an industry leader, puts
OL,9,FCornwall on the map.
OL,11,FIan first came to the site in Helston
OL,12,Fin the 1980s as a communications
OL,13,Fdesign engineer- with equipment he'd
OL,14,Fdesigned himself- to communicate with
OL,15,Fspacecraft and aeroplanes.
OL,17,F"When BT decided to rationalise its
OL,18,Fground stations, it became my quest to
OL,19,Fre-establish Goonhilly," he added.
