OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1718567067
OL,3,CMan who pioneered space communications
OL,4,Cin Cornwall awarded OBE
OL,6,F"It took a while to re-establish it
OL,7,Fand get it going, but since then we've
OL,8,Fdone some absolutely amazing things.
OL,9,FSome real world firsts, and we've
OL,10,Fcommunicated with missions around
OL,11,Fmars, we've landed spacecraft on the
OL,12,Fmoon, we've helped humans get into
OL,13,Fspace."
OL,15,FSpeaking on future work, Ian said:
OL,16,F"We're seeing NASA is really pushing
OL,17,Ffor the globalisation of moon
OL,18,Fexploration. We're helping companies
OL,19,Fdo that."
